            </div>
            <div class="key-card">
              <span class="key-number">7</span>
              <h4>Pattern Generation</h4>
              <p>
                The deepest level: creating new patterns intentionally. Not just recognizing
                collapse—designing resilience. Engineering systems that resist cascade failure.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

